<bibRefCitation author="Aukema" box="[158,382,1589,1614]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" refString="Aukema, B., Rieger, C. &amp; Rabitsch, W. (2013) Catalogue of the Heteroptera of the Palaearctic Region. Vol. 6. Supplement. Netherlands Entomological Society. Ponsen &amp; Looijen, Wageningen, 628 pp." type="book" year="2013">
